<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7256&amp;p=31267#p31267"><![CDATA[
Also, if the skin allows it, you can add icons. You can change them in the <strong>Customize Start Menu</strong> tab. Just make sure the file is a <strong>.ico</strong> file, and not a <strong>png or bmp</strong>.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=16614">AcroGen</a> — Mon Jan 16, 2017 10:45 am</p><hr />
